entries.description:
Good Areas is cricket's storyteller. Jarrod Kimber created the channel to explore the sport's best tales, from the 1700s to today.

Cricket is a game that requires digging deep, and that's what this channel does. We’ve analyzed Virat Kohli’s shot at the MCG, coined the term "Zombie ball," covered the pace-bowling pandemic, uncovered Kookaburra’s impact on cricket balls, Babar's toe, Pujara's speed, Shadab's arse, the South African World Cup curse and the tortured history of Kiwi openers. 

We tell cricket stories from any country or format, whether men’s, women’s, or amateur cricket. We love cricket; if you do too, this is your home.

entries.title: Pinaki Bhattacharya
entries.description:
Pinaki Bhattacharya, a Paris-based Bangladeshi and trained physician, is an influential blogger and social activist. In his younger years, he was part of the Leftist student movement. With 19 books to his name on Bangladesh’s political history, society, and human rights, he's become a prominent online figure. Over 1.2 million people follow his Youtube channel, and he's also active on Facebook and Twitter. His insights on Bangladesh's socio-political landscape, and broader human rights concerns in the region are widely read by students, activists, and the general public.

Professionally, Pinaki has worked as a business executive in multinational and local Bangladeshi firms. An MBA graduate from Sorbonne Business School in Paris, he's now pursuing a PhD in sustainability. He's also a marketing professional at a renowned French multinational, one of the top Fortune 500 companies.

entries.title: Bangladesh Awami League Official
entries.description:
The Bangladesh Awami League (Bengali: বাংলাদেশ আওয়ামী লীগ, romanized: Bānglādēsh Awāmī Līg, lit. 'Bangladesh People's League'), often simply called the Awami League or AL, is one of the major political parties in Bangladesh, being the ruling party since 2009. 
The party under the leadership of Sheikh Mujibur Rahman, led the struggle for independence, first through massive populist and civil disobedience movements, such as the Six Point Movement and 1971 Non-Cooperation Movement, and then during the Bangladesh Liberation War.

entries.title: Let's ask Shogo | Your Japanese friend in Kyoto
entries.description:
I’m Shogo, a Kyoto born and Hiroshima raised Japanese, that grew up in Michigan America for 6 years, and studied Mandarin in Beijing university for a year! I live in Kyoto, as I train in Kobudo (katana/staff/chain ball), Sadō (tea ceremony), Noh theatre, and Shakuhachi (bamboo flute). My dream is "to make all Japan lovers' dreams come true" by carrying on Japanese traditional culture to the next century.

In this channel, you can take a closer look at Japanese traditional culture, tips on traveling to Kyoto, and social problems in Japan. So learners and lovers of Japanese language and culture, be sure to subscribe to enjoy more content (The content of my videos are based on personal studies and experience. There is no intention of denying other theories and cultural aspects).

entries.title: Best Ever Food Review Show
entries.description:
I travel to unique parts of the world on the hunt for the best food each country has to offer and share these stories with you in my videos.

Hey, I’m Sonny! I’m from the US but currently call Vietnam home. I’ve been living in Asia for 10 years and started making food and travel videos to document my experiences. People either enjoyed my undeniable wit or enjoyed watching me eat interesting food like sea penis, and thus Best Ever Food Review Show came to be. 

Best Ever Food Review Show is the first food review show exploring the unique foods of each country with a fresh point of view and a punchy delivery, encouraging empathy and understanding of other cultures along the way. From the best street food to the most insane food markets to...well...yes, sea penis, nothing is off limits (except cucumbers. Cucumbers are off limits). 

I can’t wait to see where this food journey takes us. Don’t forget to subscribe, so we can connect through food and travel and become Bestys!

entries.title: ATN Bangla News
entries.description:
Welcome to ATN Bangla Official Youtube Channel.

ATN Bangla (Asian Television Network) is a Bengali language digital cable television channel. It transmits from its studio in Dhaka, Bangladesh.This is the first satellite based channel in Bangladesh. The channel is transmitted in South Asia, the Middle East, Europe, and North America. The channel offers a wide variety of programming including news, movies, dramas, talk shows, and more. The channel started broadcast in South Asia on 16 July 1997, though their website shows 15 July. They officially started their broadcasting on 16 July. Broadcasts to Europe began in 2001. The channel started broadcasting news from 16 August 2001.

entries.title: Al Muqaddimah
entries.description:
Salam and welcome to Al Muqaddimah! 

My name is Syawish and I'm the one-man team that runs Al Muqaddimah. History has always appealed to me more than most things and with time, I came to realize that a certain part, the real, detailed part, about people that called themselves Muslims, was barely available on youtube. It didn't take a lot of research to realize that even Muslims did not seem to know much of their history like how Islam reached the world, what happened to al-Andalus etc. Wanting to answer some of those questions, I decided to fill in the gaps with Al Muqaddimah. 

Question by question, answer by answer, this caravan of history aficionados has grown into what it is today. From the very beginning, this channel has been about history and history only. All of my videos have been and will continue to be from a liberal and secular point of view. If you are looking for a religious take on Islamic history then Al Muqaddimah is not the channel for you. 

Tuhada,
Syawish.

entries.title: The Shantonu Kaisar Show
entries.description:
আসসালামুআলাইকুম।
চেষ্টা করি। আমার চেষ্টা তাদের নিয়ে যারা দেশকে ভালোবাসে। এমন অসংখ্য মানুষ আছে, যারা কোনো রাজনৈতিক দলের সঙ্গে সম্পৃক্ত নয়। কিংবা কোনো দলের পায়ে নিজের সত্ত্বা বিক্রি করে সন্তানের মুখে ভাত দিতে চায় না। এমন হাজারো মানুষ আছে, যারা জীবনের ঊর্ধ্বে ন্যায় নীতিকে প্রাধান্য দিয়ে শুধু নিজ মাটিকে ভালোবাসে। আমি আর তারা মিলেই আমাদের চ্যানেল। 

আমি একা কখনোই কিছুই না। আমার সঙ্গে আপনি আছেন, কারণ আপনিও মাটির কাছে আমার মতো দায়বদ্ধ। 
এবং আপনিও চান বাংলাদেশ যাতে মিথ্যার কাছে পরাজিত হয়ে না যায়।

আসুন এক সঙ্গে একটা অন্যরকম মানসিকতার বাংলাদেশ গড়ি। 

আপনিই পারেন পরিবর্তন আনতে।

কেমন পরিবর্তন?

সত্য জানলেন। দেশের বিরুদ্ধে করা মিথ্যাচারের নীরব প্রতিবাদ করলেন। এটাই পরিবর্তন ভাই। 
এভাবে একদিন পরিবর্তিত হবে বাংলাদেশ। 
আসসালামুআলাইকুম।

entries.title: The Food Ranger
entries.description:
My name is Trevor James and I live to eat and travel.  I live for street food and local food, and I'm traveling to taste it. I'm a hungry traveler that's currently living abroad in Chengdu, Sichuan China,  eating as much delicious food as I can.

So far, I've eaten and filmed street food and local cuisine in China, Malaysia, Singapore, and Thailand. Eating the same food as local Chinese, Malaysian, or Thai people has showed me that it's best to travel almost solely for the food! My dream is to keep eating and traveling the world forever, a non-stop adventure!  I live to travel, and I know you do too! I love eating street foods and culinary treats while learning about new cultures!

Food is different around the world, and I want to share it with you. Food is something that connects us all, and to me, food is the best way to connect and have a true cultural experience!

for business inquires: thefoodranger@delkatalents.com

entries.title: You Knock on My Door
entries.description:
YOU KNOCK ON MY DOOR

Eda, who ties all her hopes to her education, confronts Serkan Bolat, who cuts off her international education scholarship and left her with a high school diploma. Serkan Bolat offers Eda to give her scholarship back if she pretends to be his fiance for two months. 

Although Eda rejects the offer of this man as she hates him, she has to accept it when the conditions change. While pretending to be engaged, Serkan and Eda begin to experience a passionate, challenging relationship that will make them forget all they know right. Because love is difficult. And that's why it's amazing.

To Hande Erçel and Kerem Bürsin; successful names such as Neslihan Yeldan, Bige Önal, Evrim Doğan, İsmail Ege Şaşmaz, Anıl İlter, Melisa Döngel, Çağrı Çıtanak, Elçin Afacan, Sitare Akbaş, Başak Gümülcinelioğlu, Alican Aytekin, Sarp Bozkurt, Dorukhan Kenger and İlkyaz Arslan will accompany the series.

entries.title: My Cooking House
entries.description:
আসসালামুআলাইকুম,  
আজ ৮ এপ্রিল,আলহামদুলিল্লাহ!  আল্লাহ তায়ালার অসেস রহমতে আজ 400k সদস্যের ভালবাসায় এই চ্যানেলটি তে আমি কাজ করছি। নিশ্চয়ই এতো গুলো মানুষের কাছে আমার রেসিপিগুলো ভালো লেগেছে। আপনাদের ভালোবাসায়,এবং দোয়াই আজ আমি এপর্যন্ত আসতে পেরেছি।আপনাদের কাছে আমার অনুরোধ। আপনারা আমার এবং আমার পরিবারের জন্য দোয়া করবেন প্লিজ। যখন আমি মারা যাবো,এই পৃথিবীতে আমি থাকবোনা।তবে আমার তৈরী এই রেসিপি গুলো থেকে যাবে। আপনারা যারা আমার রেসিপি গুলো দেখবেন, প্লিজ মন থেকে আমার জন্য দোয়া করে যাবেনে  । আর এই পাওয়াটাই আমার জন্য শ্রেষ্ট পাওয়া হবে।
মাঝেে মাঝে আমার মনে হয় আমি যদি এখনই মারা যায়। তাহলে আমার আরো কিছু প্রিয় রেসিপি আপনাদের সাথে শেয়ার করা বাকি থেকে যাবে। তাই আল্লাহ তায়ালার কাছে দোয়া করি, আল্লাহ তুমি আমাকে নেক হায়াত দান করো। নিশ্চয়ই আল্লাহ তায়ালা আমাকে ততোটুকুই হ্মমতা দান করবে যতো টুকু এই পৃথিবীর জন্য আমার দ্বারা মঙ্গল করা সম্ভব।আমিন।

entries.title: Bishaash
entries.description:
"Bishaash" follows the exploits of Zara, a young British woman of Bangladeshi origin who, after the death of her grandfather in London, discovers she has inherited a family stake in a mysterious detective agency based in an antique shop in Old Dhaka.  

Determined to find out more, Zara packs up her life in London and travels to Bangladesh where she meets tough young supernatural investigator Abir, and is thrown headfirst into his world of mystery, magic and adventure. 

Produced by the BBC World Service Trust  (now BBC Media Action) in both Bangla and English, "Bishaash" is part of English in Action, funded by  UKaid from the Department for International Development."Bishaash" and is the first ever supernatural detective series in south Asia.

entries.description:
Online Soccer Manager (OSM) is a free-to-play football management game for Android, iOS and Web. In this game you can become the manager of your favorite football team. 

OSM is the absolute foundation of Gamebasics Studio. Millions of players are managing their favourite club on a daily basis. It’s one of the few mobile games that has been successful for such a long period of time and is built on a unique combination of social and accessible gaming.

We believe one of the most important features of the game is the social aspect of the game. There is no single player. OSM is a fun game because you play it with others. Could be with a total stranger from the other side of the world, could be with your dearest friends and family.

Show the world that you are the best football manager!

entries.title: Karadayi Urdu * Season 1 * HD
entries.description: The story takes place during the 1970s in Istanbul. Mahir is a young and handsome man. He works as a shoe repairer and has a comfortable middle-class life. He lives happily with his family, his father, mother, two sisters and one brother. On the day of his engagement to Ayten, his perfect life turns upside down. His father, Nazif Kara, is blamed for a murder. His father is convicted of murdering the Chief Prosecutor and he is sentenced to death after the trial. The witnesses saw Nazif Kara on crime scene with the weapon in his hands.The Kara family's life is then turned upside down because of a wrong accusation that results in the imprisonment of Nazif Kara for what he didn't commit. Mahir never believes that his father is guilty. He tries to prove it and wants to give him his freedom. However, finding any evidence to save his father would be too hard for him.
